metadata.description:
üåü All collectors who share their 2023 New Year's Resolution in a comment are eligible for an airdrop from my Sound collection üåü

Lots of things changed for me in 2022.

I moved to Brooklyn, switched careers, ended a long-term relationship, quit weed, traveled everywhere from Paris to Bogot√°, moved OUT of Brooklyn, released my debut single and genesis music NFTs...you get the point.

In the midst of all of this I have attempted to become more discerning in my day to day life. Every day brings new decisions. How will I show up for myself? Which relationships will I prioritize? Which habits will I direct my time and energy to?

NOT4ME was my first attempt to answer these questions as I began to face my vices, cut my losses and chart a course for healing. I am grateful for the chance to share this stripped down version of NOT4ME for the first time here on Sound, and I hope you enjoy ‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî•

Written & performed by AL3C
Mixed by Mixed Emotions Music

I don't wanna keep on playing, and I don't wanna feel ashamed
